{"tid":1464901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼唔越捉越少 就好似無執任證咁","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:14.000Z","uid":236709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4e61098e895a9a06e6bc1101800fc5b691f277","tid":1464901,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">呢幾日<br />\n會係最多鬼既時候</span><br />\n<br />\n記住星期日係咩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係818民陣遊行呀</span></strong><br />\n我係林奠老閪都阻止啦<br />\n出鬼打散你地<br />\n整臭你地個名<br />\n星期日就冇人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼出左比你發現<br />\n黃左一次兩次三次<br />\n無恥則敵<br />\n就好似無執任證咁<br />\n<br />\n所以出鬼佢地冇所謂<br />\n人眼知又點吹我漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼只會越黎越多</span></strong><br />\n由其呢幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家小心<br />\n<br />\n大家可以討論<br />\n可以改下一場行動點樣做<br />\n可以停一停保守D同818集氣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但絕對唔好分化<br />\n團結係我地最大既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"218595194ca38eb8da21755f3a7350ccbd54b89a","tid":1464901,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e974c264792aa72fda1f2592513e3cb3f0755d64","tid":1464901,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93ac18d9a2af43cde1f5f589b4d8788c34173df","tid":1464901,"uid":79278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e4e61098e895a9a06e6bc1101800fc5b691f277","tid":1464901,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">呢幾日<br />\n會係最多鬼既時候</span><br />\n<br />\n記住星期日係咩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx